Project Gado for Linux
======================

Requirements:

* Python 2.7
* PyGame 1.9.1
* PIL (Python Imaging Library)
* PySane
* PySerial


Instructions:
You can run gadoMain.py to have a test run where the robot picks up from the stack, scans the artifact and puts it in the discard pile. Please check the different values for the robot arm.

You can use testRobot.py to easily know which values are good for your set-up or test the different parts of Gado.

Changelog:

-Version 0.2:
* Small utilities to test the Gado robot
-Version 0.1:
* Refactor, tidy up and make a robust interface to interact with the webcam and the scanner
